longBusinessSummary: Braime Group PLC, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the distribution of bulk material handling components and monitoring equipment in the United Kingdom, rest of Europe, the Americas, Africa, Australia, and Asia. It manufactures and sells deep drawn metal presswork products. The company was formerly known as T.F. & J.H. Braime (Holdings) P.L.C. and changed its name to Braime Group PLC in August 2019. The company was founded in 1888 and is headquartered in Leeds, the United Kingdom.
